{"tid":2530873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國武漢突發「9級龍捲風」 41人受傷、6人失聯","createTime":"2021-05-14T18:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T20:17:07.000Z","uid":276273,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc6e57805bd662e88e18c33e44bab3f6553f38b","tid":2530873,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T18:30:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3532977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3532977&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOoUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=9a6e45c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3532977&h=b220b856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3532977</a><br />\n<br />\n2021/05/15 02:17  <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國武漢14日晚間8點39分突發9級龍捲風，跟據官方初步統計，災害造成41人受傷，6人失聯，暫時無人死亡。<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，武漢蔡甸區14日晚間突發龍捲風，風速達到每秒23.9公尺，破壞力驚人，當場造成多處民房受損，並且有多名民眾受傷，當地政府目前正組織救災隊伍深入災區，聲稱要盡可能減少傷亡，災區最新畫面曝光後引發中國網友議論。<br />\n中國武漢本月10日也出現強烈暴風，官方資料顯示，當天下午刮起的「10級雷暴大風」，造成北高藝裝飾工程有限公司2名洗窗工人的吊籃被狂風吹起劇烈晃動，多次撞擊大樓玻璃帷幕牆，導致玻璃碎片四濺，兩人最終送醫不治身亡；當天的劇烈天氣也造成車站候車大廳淹水，街道出現冰雹。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O963oPbAuGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO963oPbAuGg&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOoUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=7228caba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O963oPbAuGg</a>"},{"pid":"9de7d58e223115facf039e0c95601cffb82622db","tid":2530873,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T18:34:30.000Z","msg":"[有片] 史上最刺激海盗船<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2530826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2530826</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢獨家"},{"pid":"c9dfe1fb4067278ef3fde84e6bff83fe94cc0a17","tid":2530873,"uid":48889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T18:35:21.000Z",